title: IPackAndGo.GetDocumentNames
description: Gets the original paths and filenames of all of the model's documents for Pack and Go.

parameters.name: DocumentNames
parameters.description: Array of strings of the original paths and filenames of all of the model's documents

returns: True if the original paths and filenames of all of the model's documents are returned, false if not
remarks:
To get the drawing documents of the model, set
IPackAndGo::IncludeDrawings
to true; otherwise, the paths and filenames of the model's drawing documents are not returned.
